<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Landscaping &amp; External Works</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Soft Landscaping</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Soft landscaping across London and the South East — planting, beds and turfing, topsoil and ground prep, trees, hedging and screening, installed to BS 4428 and nursed through establishment. Planting that's established, not just planted, at handover — with the records to discharge planning landscape conditions.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Soft Landscaping →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Soft Landscaping,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Planting, beds &amp; turfing</li><li>Topsoil &amp; ground prep</li><li>Trees, hedging &amp; screening</li><li>Irrigation &amp; establishment</li><li>Native planting &amp; habitat features</li><li>Maintenance records &amp; as-builts</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 4428 — general landscape operations</li><li>BS 5837 — trees in relation to design, demolition &amp; construction</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you maintain planting after install?</summary><p>Yes. New planting and turf are installed to BS 4428, then carried through a defined establishment period — watering, weeding and replacement of failures — so the soft landscaping is established, not just planted, at handover.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you protect existing trees during construction?</summary><p>We work to BS 5837 for trees in relation to design and construction — root protection areas, no-dig methods and protective fencing around retained trees — so existing planting survives the works and new trees are set out to establish well.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you help discharge planning landscape conditions and biodiversity net gain?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver the landscape works that discharge planning conditions and support biodiversity net-gain commitments — native planting, habitat features and the records to evidence them — alongside the landscape architect and ecologist where one is appointed.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Landscaping &amp; External Works</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; External Works overview</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/hard-landscaping/">Hard Landscaping</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/surfacing/">Surfacing &amp; Access</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/boundaries/">Boundaries &amp; Features</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name"